PrecisINDIAN BRIDGE WORKERS REMISSION ORDER - which provides for the remission of income tax payable by Indians for the years 1984 to 1991 on earnings paid by an office of the Seaway International Bridge Corporation, Ltd. located on Cornwall Island in respect of their employment at the international bridges on Cornwall Island (Akwesasne Indian Reserve).
